snippet.title: Flick Golf! Free: iOS & Android
snippet.description:
Download for free today!
  http://bit.ly/i_fgfree
► http://bit.ly/gp_freegolf

"Impossible to put down”
- Eurogamer

Play the App Store’s biggest arcade golf hit! 
#1 Sports Game in over 100 Countries! 

NO CLUBS REQUIRED 
Flick your balls to sink a perfect hole-in-one! Add spin and curve using our signature after-touch controls.

THREE UNIQUE GAME MODES
Beat high scores across 15 beautiful courses set in amazing locations across the globe.

WATCH OUT FOR HAZARDS! 
Bunkers, trees, water and wind will test your mettle as you drive for the high score.

NEW ELIMINATOR MODE
How many consecutive hole-in-ones can you hit?
